    <CiWall1 :x="5*dx" :y="8*dy" sid="w" dir="h11v+"></CiWall1>

    <!--Reihe 9-->
    <CiWall1 :x="11*dx" :y="9*dy" sid="w" dir="v+v-11h+"></CiWall1>
    <CiWall1 :x="16*dx" :y="9*dy" sid="w" dir="h-7"></CiWall1>

    <CiWall1 :x="13*dx" :y="11*dy" sid="w" dir="h5v-"></CiWall1>
    <CiWall1 :x="16*dx" :y="11*dy" sid="w" dir="h-"></CiWall1>
    <!--Reihe 13-->

    <text @click="showErdgeschoss()" x="1355" y="765" textLength="190" lengthAdjust="spacingAndGlyphs" class="styleStiege">Erdge-</text>
    <text @click="showErdgeschoss()" x="1355" y="865" textLength="190" lengthAdjust="spacingAndGlyphs" class="styleStiege">schoss</text>
  </svg>
</template>

<script lang="ts">
import { defineComponent } from 'vue'
import { Geo } from '../classes/Geo'
import CiButton1 from '@/components/CiButton1.vue'
import CiButton2 from '@/components/CiButton2.vue'
import CiLamp1 from '@/components/CiLamp1.vue'
import CiSocket1 from '@/components/CiSocket1.vue'
import CiWall1 from '@/components/CiWall1.vue'
import CiWindow1 from '@/components/CiWindow1.vue'

// import CiWeather from '@/components/CiWeather.vue'
// import CiDoor from '@/components/CiDoor.vue'
// import CiMotion from '@/components/CiMotion.vue'

export default defineComponent({
  name: 'Erdgeschoss',
  components: {
    CiButton1,
    CiButton2,
    CiLamp1,
    CiSocket1,
    CiWall1,
    CiWindow1
    // CiWeather,
    // CiDoor,
    // CiMotion

  },
  computed: {
    geo: function (): Geo {
      const geo1 = new Geo(0, 0)
      return geo1
    },
    dx: function (): number { return (this.geo.dxo()) },
    dy: function (): number { return (this.geo.dyo()) }
  },
  methods: {
    showErdgeschoss: function () {
      console.log('CLICK - showErdgeschoss', '')
      return this.$router.push({ name: 'Erdgeschoss' })
    }
  }
})
</script>

<style scoped>
 .styleStiege { font: bold 60px sans-serif; fill: red; cursor: pointer; }

 #e2su {
   cursor: pointer;
 }
</style>
